                    <span>Gandhi found this translation of the Gita to be the best he was able to find.  Little more need be said.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The classic translation in affordable format.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
